data.description: Magnificent home with Pool and, 4 Bedrooms and an office, 2.Bath split floor with gas fireplace. From the welcoming curb appeal to the huge living room. YOU WILL LOVE EVERYTHING ABOUT THIS HOME!!! Tile and hardwood floors throughout the house (NO CARPET) , roof in 2013, A/C 2013. Lots of windows to let the natural light shine in. 2 cars over-sized garage, living, family and dining room, huge kitchen with eat in nook. The master suite has 2 walk-in closets, double sink vanity. YOU MUST SEE IT!!! All of the large ticket items have been addressed so there is nothing to accomplish but hand over the keys and move in, or collect the rent! Close to Rt 1 entrance so you can take a trip to the oldest city St Augustine, or Daytona Beach to relax on the Beach or enjoy Bike week or the famous Daytona 500 Speedway. Schedule a showing today, don't miss this opportunity.
